Package: SGPreports
Type: Package
Title: Reports rendered in multiple formats using a single function and R Markdown file.
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-4-7
Authors@R: c(person(given=c("Adam", "R."), family="Van Iwaarden", email="avaniwaarden@gmail.com", role=c("aut", "cre")),
		person(given=c("Damian", "W."), family="Betebenner", email="dbetebenner@nciea.org", role="aut")) 
Maintainer: Adam Van Iwaarden <avaniwaarden@gmail.com>
Description: Provides Rmarkdown templates for the creation of reproducible reports in multiple formats, including technical reports for SGP analyses.
Depends: R (>= 3.0), rmarkdown (>= 0.5.1)
Imports: Hmisc, Grmd, Gmisc, htmlTable, jpeg
SystemRequirements: pandoc (>= 1.12.3) - http://johnmacfarlane.net/pandoc
